Package org.azeckoski.reflectutils.refmap

A map for holding soft/weak references to objects (key and values)

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ReferenceMap.Strategy  
 

Class Summary
FinalizableSoftReference<T> Soft reference with a FinalizableReference.finalizeReferent() method which a background thread invokes after the garbage collector reclaims the referent.
FinalizableWeakReference<T> Weak reference with a FinalizableReference.finalizeReferent() method which a background thread invokes after the garbage collector reclaims the referent.
ReferenceMap<K,V> Concurrent hash map that wraps keys and/or values in soft or weak references.
